---
import Base from "../layouts/base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How Clarity. collects, uses, and protects your data."
  type="WebPage"
  canonicalURL="https://getclarity.win/privacy-policy"
>
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-20">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
      Effective date: <strong>13 June 2025</strong><br />
      Last updated: <strong>13 June 2025</strong>
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">
      1. What information we collect
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-4">We collect the following personal data:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
      <li>Email address when you join the waitlist or request a proposal</li>
      <li>Name and organisation details if voluntarily provided</li>
      <li>Billing information (handled via Stripe)</li>
      <li>Communication history via email</li>
      <li>Technical info (IP address, browser type, etc.) from logs</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-6">We do not use cookies or tracking pixels at this time.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">
      2. How we use your information
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      We use your data to:
      <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Register you on our waitlist and send confirmation emails</li>
        <li>Respond to your requests and provide early access</li>
        <li>Fulfil billing and invoicing requirements</li>
        <li>Improve our services based on anonymised data</li>
      </ul>
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">
      3. Legal basis for processing
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      We process your data based on:
      <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Consent</strong> – when you sign up or submit a form</li>
        <li><strong>Contract</strong> – when delivering services to you</li>
        <li>
          <strong>Legitimate interest</strong> – for site operations and improvement
        </li>
      </ul>
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">
      4. How your data is stored
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      Your data is securely stored using:
      <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>AWS DynamoDB for waitlist and form data</li>
        <li>AWS SES for email delivery</li>
        <li>Airtable for internal tracking</li>
        <li>Stripe for secure payment processing</li>
      </ul>
      Access is limited to the Clarity. team only.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">5. Data retention</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      We retain data only as long as needed:
      <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>
          Waitlist data: deleted after 12 months of inactivity or upon request
        </li>
        <li>Billing records: retained for legal and accounting requirements</li>
      </ul>
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">6. Your rights</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      Under the UK and EU GDPR, you have the right to:
      <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Access the data we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request corrections</li>
        <li>Request deletion</li>
        <li>Object to processing in certain cases</li>
      </ul>
      To make a request, email <strong>privacy@getclarity.win</strong>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">
      7. International transfers
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      Data is hosted in UK/EU-compliant AWS regions. If transfers outside these
      regions occur, we ensure safeguards are in place.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">8. Contact us</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      For any questions or concerns:
      <br />
      <strong>Clarity. Privacy Team</strong><br />
      Email: privacy@getclarity.win
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>
